  "items": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "question": "What is Sale Locator?",
      "answer": "Sale Locator helps you discover the best nearby sales, trending discounts, flash offers, and store promotions in your city all in one place."
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "question": "How do I find deals near my location?",
      "answer": "You can allow location access or manually select your city. We then show nearby store offers, trending discounts, and relevant local deals."
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "question": "Are the deals and offers updated regularly?",
      "answer": "Yes, deals are updated frequently to make sure you always see the latest flash sales, seasonal discounts, and active store promotions."
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "question": "Do I need to create an account to use Sale Locator?",
      "answer": "No, you can browse sales and explore offers without creating an account. Subscribing with email helps you receive deal alerts."
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "question": "Can I use Sale Locator on mobile devices?",
      "answer": "Yes, Sale Locator is fully responsive and works smoothly on mobile phones, tablets, laptops, and desktop screens."
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "question": "What kind of deals can I find here?",
      "answer": "You can explore electronics offers, fashion discounts, beauty deals, home essentials, trending flash sales, and nearby local store promotions."
